yball scouts, including one, she said, from NCAA's University of Perpetual Help.\", \"from\": 314, \"to\": 484, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 348, \"end\": 361, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Camarines_Sur\", \"score\": 0.999999991754521, \"rank\": 8.24569770319608e-09, \"text\": \"Camarines Sur\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Camarines_Sur\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Camarines_Sur\"}, {\"begin\": 448, \"end\": 452, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"score\": 0.9998896618931151, \"rank\": 9.957114205788016e-05, \"text\": \"NCAA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/National_Collegiate_Athletic_Association\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a setter\", \"from\": 335, \"to\": 343}, {\"ngram\": \"the Palarong Pambansa\", \"from\": 365, \"to\": 386}, {\"ngram\": \"volleyball scouts\", \"from\": 399, \"to\": 416}, {\"ngram\": \"Perpetual Help\", \"from\": 469, \"to\": 483}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite receiving interest, Delgaco, who eventually became thefirst Filipina rowerto qualify in the country's100-year historyin the Olympics, felt her chance to shine in volleyball was slim.\", \"from\": 486, \"to\": 676, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 554, \"end\": 562, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipinos\", \"score\": 0.9171481179897879, \"rank\": 0.0903364248205323, \"text\": \"Filipina\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipinos\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Filipinos\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"interest\", \"from\": 504, \"to\": 512}, {\"ngram\": \"Delgaco\", \"from\": 514, \"to\": 521}, {\"ngram\": \"the country's100-year historyin\", \"from\": 582, \"to\": 613}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 626}, {\"ngram\": \"her chance\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 643}, {\"ngram\": \"volleyball\", \"from\": 656, \"to\": 666}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"In volleyball back then, I could not see myself excelling [long-term],\\\" Delgaco said in Filipino.\", \"from\": 678, \"to\": 776, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"volleyball\", \"from\": 682, \"to\": 692}, {\"ngram\": \"Delgaco\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 758}, {\"ngram\": \"Filipino\", \"from\": 767, \"to\": 775}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From age 11 to 17, Delgaco had a volleyball career in sight, even idolizing former UAAP star Alyssa Valdez.\", \"from\": 778, \"to\": 885, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 871, \"end\": 877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alyssa_Anderson\", \"score\": 0.9999999958877197, \"rank\": 3.616489586652383e-09, \"text\": \"Alyssa\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10843402\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alyssa_Anderson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alyssa_Anderson\"}, {\"begin\": 878, \"end\": 884, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Framber_Valdez\", \"score\": 0.9216031002264942, \"rank\": 0.08506578929649662, \"text\": \"Valdez\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q10871364\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Framber_Valdez\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Framber_Valdez\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"age\", \"from\": 783, \"to\": 786}, {\"ngram\": \"Delgaco\", \"from\": 797, \"to\": 804}, {\"ngram\": \"a volleyball career\", \"from\": 809, \"to\": 828}, {\"ngram\": \"sight\", \"from\": 832, \"to\": 837}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But eventually, the Iriga native gave herself a reality check.\", \"from\": 886, \"to\": 948, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 906, \"end\": 911, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iriga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5850204968656855e-22, \"text\": \"Iriga\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iriga\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Iriga\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a reality check\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 947}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She felt the need to try something new, so when an opportunity to try out and train for a different sport in Manila came, a teenaged Delgaco took a leap of faith.\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 1112, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1059, \"end\": 1065, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metro_Manila\", \"score\": 0.8801492919596358, \"rank\": 0.13617088502515218, \"text\": \"Manila\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metro_Manila\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metro_Manila\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the need\", \"from\": 959, \"to\": 967}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 975, \"to\": 984}, {\"ngram\": \"an opportunity\", \"from\": 998, \"to\": 1012}, {\"ngram\": \"a different sport\", \"from\": 1038, \"to\": 1055}, {\"ngram\": \"a teenaged Delgaco\", \"from\": 1072, \"to\": 1090}, {\"ngram\": \"a leap\", \"from\": 1096, \"to\": 1102}, {\"ngram\": \"faith\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1111}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Convinced by a rowing coach, Delgaco jumped into her new sport, betting on her physical tools and innate strength, which her mentors believed to be her biggest asset.\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1280, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a rowing coach\", \"from\": 1127, \"to\": 1141}, {\"ngram\": \"Delgaco\", \"from\": 1143, \"to\": 1150}, {\"ngram\": \"her new sport\", \"from\": 1163, \"to\": 1176}, {\"ngram\": \"her physical tools\", \"from\": 1189, \"to\": 1207}, {\"ngram\": \"strength\", \"from\": 1219, \"to\": 1227}, {\"ngram\": \"her mentors\", \"from\": 1235, \"to\": 1246}, {\"ngram\": \"her biggest asset\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1279}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He really talked to me and my parents.\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1321, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my parents\", \"from\": 1310, \"to\": 1320}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I said alright, if I could do well in rowing, maybe this is really for me,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1407, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"rowing\", \"from\": 1360, \"to\": 1366}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Starting without any knowledge of the sport, Delgaco traveled to Manila for the first time in her life.\", \"from\": 1409, \"to\": 1512, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1474, \"end\": 1480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metro_Manila\", \"score\": 0.8801492919596358, \"rank\": 0.13617088502515218, \"text\": \"Manila\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metro_Manila\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Metro_Manila\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any knowledge\", \"from\": 1426, \"to\": 1439}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1443, \"to\": 1452}, {\"ngram\": \"Delgaco\", \"from\": 1454, \"to\": 1461}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 1485, \"to\": 1499}, {\"ngram\": \"her life\", \"from\": 1503, \"to\": 1511}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She did not even bring a travel bag with her, using instead a cardboard box to pack her clothes and relocate to the city.\", \"from\": 1513, \"to\": 1634, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a travel bag\", \"from\": 1536, \"to\": 1548}, {\"ngram\": \"a cardboard box\", \"from\": 1573, \"to\": 1588}, {\"ngram\": \"her clothes\", \"from\": 1597, \"to\": 1608}, {\"ngram\": \"the city\", \"from\": 1625, \"to\": 1633}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Slowly, she grasped the fundamentals of rowing, building herself up to go for an Olympic standard 2,000-meter race.\", \"from\": 1636, \"to\": 1751, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the fundamentals\", \"from\": 1656, \"to\": 1672}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic standard 2,000-meter race\", \"from\": 1714, \"to\": 1750}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rowing techniques included sculling backward, requiring leg and arm strength in pulling back the paddle - a stark contrast to dragon boat, which propels the boat forward.\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1924, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Rowing techniques\", \"from\": 1753, \"to\": 1770}, {\"ngram\": \"leg\", \"from\": 1809, \"to\": 1812}, {\"ngram\": \"arm strength\", \"from\": 1817, \"to\": 1829}, {\"ngram\": \"the paddle\", \"from\": 1846, \"to\": 1856}, {\"ngram\": \"a stark contrast\", \"from\": 1859, \"to\": 1875}, {\"ngram\": \"dragon boat\", \"from\": 1879, \"to\": 1890}, {\"ngram\": \"the boat\", \"from\": 1906, \"to\": 1914}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From orchestrating plays for her volleyball team, Delgaco aced captaining her racing shell, the term used for competitive rowing boats.\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 2061, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"plays\", \"from\": 1945, \"to\": 1950}, {\"ngram\": \"her volleyball team\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 1974}, {\"ngram\": \"Delgaco\", \"from\": 1976, \"to\": 1983}, {\"ngram\": \"her racing shell\", \"from\": 2000, \"to\": 2016}, {\"ngram\": \"competitive rowing boats\", \"from\": 2036, \"to\": 2060}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"When I started rowing, in under one year, I already won a medal,\\\" shared Delgaco.\", \"from\": 2063, \"to\": 2145, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"one year\", \"from\": 2096, \"to\": 2104}, {\"ngram\": \"a medal\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2127}, {\"ngram\": \"Delgaco\", \"from\": 2137, \"to\": 2144}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That's when I felt like this is where I am going to excel.\", \"from\": 2146, \"to\": 2205, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"And then, every year after that, the blessings did not stop.\\\"\", \"from\": 2206, \"to\": 2267, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the blessings\", \"from\": 2239, \"to\": 2252}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By 2024, her biggest blessing came.\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2304, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her biggest blessing\", \"from\": 2278, \"to\": 2298}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Delgaco booked a ticket to the Paris Olympics after placing fourth in the women's single sculls in the World Rowing Asian and Oceanian Qualification Regatta in Chungju, South Korea, last April 21.\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2501, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2408, \"end\": 2420, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Rowing_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"World Rowing\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Rowing_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Rowing_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 2421, \"end\": 2426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"score\": 0.9999999999936335, \"rank\": 6.427534544507309e-12, \"text\": \"Asian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Asian_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 2465, \"end\": 2472, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chungju\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2093732954744546e-19, \"text\": \"Chungju\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chungju\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chungju\"}, {\"begin\": 2474, \"end\": 2485, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"score\": 0.9996862226409672, \"rank\": 0.0003138588027896873, \"text\": \"South Korea\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/South_Korea\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Delgaco\", \"from\": 2305, \"to\": 2312}, {\"ngram\": \"a ticket\", \"from\": 2320, \"to\": 2328}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 2332, \"to\": 2350}, {\"ngram\": \"the women's single sculls\", \"from\": 2375, \"to\": 2400}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The feat made her only the fourth rower - and just the first female - in Philippine history to advance to the Olympic games after Edgardo Maerina (1988 Seoul Games), Benjamin Tolentino Jr. (2000 Sydney Games), and Cris Nievarez (2022 Tokyo Games).\", \"from\": 2503, \"to\": 2750, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2669, \"