 Games\", \"from\": 3391, \"to\": 3414}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But whichever way her campaigns end up, Delgaco always makes sure to represent the country well.\", \"from\": 3436, \"to\": 3532, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her campaigns\", \"from\": 3454, \"to\": 3467}, {\"ngram\": \"Delgaco\", \"from\": 3476, \"to\": 3483}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 3515, \"to\": 3526}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More so now that she's in the sport's biggest stage.\", \"from\": 3533, \"to\": 3585, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sport's biggest stage\", \"from\": 3559, \"to\": 3584}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Bihira lang mga atletang nakakapasok dito sa Olympic competition(It's rare to be a part of this),\\\" said Delgaco.- Rappler.com How does this make you feel?\", \"from\": 3587, \"to\": 3743, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3702, \"end\": 3713, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rappler.com\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rappler\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Bihira lang mga atletang\", \"from\": 3588, \"to\": 3612}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic competition(It's rare\", \"from\": 3633, \"to\": 3662}, {\"ngram\": \"a part\", \"from\": 3669, \"to\": 3675}]}, {\"sentence\": \"follow us\", \"from\": 3745, \"to\": 3754, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 3752, \"to\": 3754}]}]}"